inputs.text: A sprawling cyberpunk metropolis at night, illuminated by neon signs in vibrant pink, blue, and green. Towering skyscrapers with holographic advertisements loom over the rain-soaked streets, where people in futuristic attire walk past high-tech market stalls. Flying cars hover above the city, leaving behind glowing trails. Cybernetic street samurais and AI-controlled drones patrol the alleys, while a giant digital billboard displays a glitching face of an artificial intelligence overlord. The atmosphere is hazy with a mix of fog and digital distortion, creating a moody, cinematic effect. The scene is highly detailed, with reflections in the wet pavement and intricate cybernetic enhancements on pedestrians. Hyper-realistic, ultra-detailed, cinematic lighting, 8K resolution, sci-fi noir aesthetic.
